          <title>
            <string language="sv">Allt finns kvar</string>
            <string language="en">Everything is left</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Alles wird gelassen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Tout est laissé</string>

          <description>
            <string language="sv">Kretsloppen i naturen fungerar så att organiska ämnen bryts ner och byggs upp hela tiden. Modul 7 - Allt finns kvar.Naturkunskap A - Åsö.</string>
            <string language="en">The cycles in the nature function so that organic matters are broken down and is built up all the time. 

Module 7 - everything is left.

Naturkunskap A - Åsö.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Die Schleifen in der Natur arbeiten, damit 
organische Stoffe unterbrochener Abstieg sind und die ganze Zeit 
aufgebaut werden. Modul 7 - alles ist left.Naturkunskap A - 
Åsö.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les cycles dans la nature fonctionnent de sorte 
que des sujets organiques soient décomposés et sont accumulés toute
l'heure. Module 7 - tout est left.Naturkunskap A - Åsö.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Os ciclos na natureza funcionam de modo que as 
matérias orgânicas sejam pena quebrada e sejam construídas acima de
toda a hora. Módulo 7 - tudo é left.Naturkunskap A - Åsö.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">I cicli nella natura funzionano in moda da 
suddividere gli argomenti organici ed è accumulato tutto il tempo. 
Modulo 7 - tutto è left.Naturkunskap A - Åsö.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Οι κύκλοι στη φύση λειτουργούν έτσι ώστε οι 
οργανικές ουσίες χωρίζονται και ενισχύονται όλη την ώρα. 
Ενότητα 7 - όλα αφήνονται Naturkunskap Α - Εsφ.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Los ciclos en la naturaleza funcionan para 
analizar materias orgánicas y se acumulan toda la hora. Módulo
7 - todo es left.Naturkunskap A - Åsö.</string>
          </description>
